The package boost-stl-interfaces is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS stl_interfaces)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::stl_interfaces)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_stl_interfaces REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::stl_interfaces)
